content.description:
An interesting feature that hosts two classic lines. This is long crevice of sorts that is easy to get to but also easy to overlook. There is potential for development beyond the two obvious established lines.

 The two established lines are:

 The Full Deli Sandwich - v9 - this is the left line on the top of the hill starting below the obvious hole in the wall Unknown Named - v5 - this is the obvious fissure/flake line on the right

 The nature of the crevice like location can make the problems difficult to work if you just have one pad and no spotters.
